
= The Participatory Open Online Course organized by Media@McGill , started October 2013

URL = http://www.pcond.ca/pooc/


=Description=

"Media@McGill’s Participatory, Open, Online Course (or "POOC") on The Participatory Condition addresses the history, problems and possibilities of participatory media in contemporary society.

The POOC is offered as a complement to Media@McGill’s international colloquium on The Participatory Condition, taking place in Montreal on November 15th and 16th, 2013. All participants who register for the POOC are invited to learn, share, collaborate and create knowledge using the POOC’s digital platform. Participants of all levels are welcome.

Online registration is open from September 24 to October 28, 2013."


